sub_title: Strategic thinker with a love for travel and a drive for business excellence
summary:
Tourism organizer with the goal of working in the event management field or in the field of MICE tourism.

I am a very reliable, organized, and proactive individual, that can work both in a team and individually. I am also very communicative and customer-oriented. At work, I enjoy completing tasks efficiently and on time. I am proficient in the English, Slovenian, and Serbo - Croatian languages and have a basic knowledge of the German Language at the A2 level.

With the desire to learn the field firsthand, I've helped carry out many major national and international sporting events such as the 2019 European Volleyball Championship, 2 World Cup events in Sports Gymnastics, and the 2019 Slovenian Final Four Basketball tournament.
